Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天開始就是合宿了麼  是要去哪兒來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:18.62,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：JAXA即日本宇宙航空研究開發機構
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:18.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地質標本館和JAXA  是遠藤老師提議的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真好啊  連我的那一份也好好盡興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,還有悄悄的把大家的睡臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:30.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,火箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:35.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個是在科學館裡的實物比例模型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老師對這一帶很熟悉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:41.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,算是吧  高中的時候住過這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:44.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是什麼  像機器人一樣的車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,吵死了  路都走錯了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,===op===
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.70,Asteroid - title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1100,0)\blur15\pos(600.933,921.466)}04.心跳不止！夏季合宿！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,難得見你這麼興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,跟平時一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石頭標本什麼的我也經常在書上看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,學姐學姐  看這個好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:32.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,螳螂蛻下的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:36.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.90,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.30,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,突然怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:47.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,關於暑假合宿  遠藤老師說有個很好的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要不要去我奶奶家？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哇  這表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒  我是在想這樣省下住宿費
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:59.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去參觀附近的各種地方怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:00.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,各種地方？
