Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:05.03,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1147.2,626.8)}JAXA\N宇宙中心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:05.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比如說  JAXA宇宙中心  地質標本館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以及地質公園啥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,決定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好多石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,礦物和化石都有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個  就跟圖鑑裡的石頭一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:27.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小豬豬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看到櫻學姐這麼開心  我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我們稍微退遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:35.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,找到什麼在意的東西麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:41.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石頭裡嵌了金閃閃的骰子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:46.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這邊是心型的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這麼漂亮的形狀  究竟是怎麼形成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,山梨縣石？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:04:00.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在各地發現的有特點的石頭會被認定為「縣石」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我比較中意的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,櫻石？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  這是京都石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,現在還是天然紀念物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的就像櫻花的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,非常可愛而稀少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可謂是「高嶺之花」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就如同櫻學姐一樣的令人憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:25.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感覺地質班的情緒真是高漲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老師在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好多寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這些全部加起來值多少錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,夢露學姐  那邊的展物是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,食慾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大…大家盡興的方式真是各不相同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一天還真是看不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好想一直待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  石頭你帶來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:20.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,其實上次我們在河邊燒烤那回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈撿到的泥岩說不定是化石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,於是就想要去鑑定一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,摔了一跤把石頭給摔開了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哇這是啥  好嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石1號…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  你調查了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因為不太確定是不是化石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就打算先自己研究一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這本書非常淺顯易懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  看上去真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,繪本…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想想  首先動物和植物死後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,馬上就被泥沙給埋住了這點很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:05.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不然的話就會被其他的動物吃掉或者腐爛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,然後  被泥的重量給壓住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,或是與礦物進行結合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,經過數萬年後就形成了化石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,據最近的研究發現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好像數周內就能形成哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  現在馬上就把我埋下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就能作為今年文化祭的展品了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.69,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(860.2,678.467)}米菈的\N化石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:22.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那可成大事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是真是驚人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,竟然從河邊石頭裡發現化石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也不是那麼少見的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:33.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只有有沉積岩的地方  哪兒都有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這些都是小櫻找到的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個和這個之外的都是在科學館買的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,櫻學姐太誠實了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:47.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,總之  說不定是時隔數萬年才重見天日的化石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:51.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是很想去弄清楚究竟是什麼東西麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們這表情是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,快  抓緊時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是在河邊撿的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是在河灘的哪一片區域撿到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想想  應該是在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:15.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個  這是很久以前樹葉的化石嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂  稍微安靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:21.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個黑色的痕紋  說不定不是化石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是剛剛櫻學姐都一口咬定那麼說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,安靜點啊我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們聽說過「忍石」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,忍石？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:37.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  也叫作「樹枝石」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在石頭縫隙中混入了錳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就會變成植物一樣的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:47.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因為很容易和化石搞混  所以也被叫做「假化石」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,假的化石…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不  但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:52.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.32,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HE0F2CB&\4c&HE0F2CB&\b1\frz350\pos(780,711)}鱗片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大概三厘米大小  有些發光的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這應該是魚的鱗片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,還有些更小的很難看清的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在這標籤的前面有幾條小的紋路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:05.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能看清嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,用這個來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個大概是海綿動物的骨針
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:18.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是在前寒武紀末期生活在海裡的生物的骨組織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,雖然很小  但這也是了不起的化石哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:22.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石化石…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:33.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,給你們這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是發現那個石頭周邊的地質圖解說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地層的名字以及歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,連容易找到的化石也標了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這份資料在網上也能查閱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要學一下怎麼查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地質班睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因為情報量太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,特別是小櫻  鬧盡興了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:02.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像小孩一樣  比平時還可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,櫻學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全叫不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:15.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你也不是小孩了稍微走兩步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:18.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,幸  還有學生們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,歡迎  路程辛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  你看老爺爺的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.72,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.70,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:27.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,JAXA？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,難道說老爺爺是那兒的職員？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是感覺字體有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.72,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,JA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,農協？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是喜歡宇宙的農家老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,稍微寬容一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:48.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我們是星咲高中地學部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.02,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.97\pos(420,516)}收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.02,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1408,330)}我們在尋找小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好像是合宿前兩人想出來的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在宇宙中心那麼做  看上去只像是在胡鬧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是被搭話了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,拿到糖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,參觀學習的集合點在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:14.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,爺爺似乎很想來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一起來不是也挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事  這是屬於你們的合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,火箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,昨天看到的雖然是模型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是連內部都有做的真正的火箭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:33.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真正的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我說夢露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,天文班也太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:42.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你也有點部長的樣子稍微管管…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇宙好遙遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家關係很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:54.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊  藍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是宇宙中心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能不能找到關於發現小行星的線索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們倆  對小行星感興趣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:09.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,討厭啦老師  入部那一天不是就說過的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,學姐  來拍紀念照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,歡迎大家參加參觀學習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,首先請觀看介紹影片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:31.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這兒是日本離宇宙最近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到宇宙中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在這裡將為你介紹JAXA的各種項目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇宙太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,人類太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小米菈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這又不是那種催人淚下的影片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,上了年紀真是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我們原來是少數派麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:00.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,接下來將參觀宇航員養成樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:04.27,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,通常的話只能是員工進入的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:05.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,夢露學姐  表情變得比平時認真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.50,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,所以請大家緊緊跟隨我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:08.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,應該有很多想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,畢竟這是她嚮往的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嚮往？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這邊的宇航服約重120千克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:20.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,配備有生命維持裝置  氧氣以及電池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.75,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,當然  在艙外活動時…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,窗戶裡邊是封閉壞境的訓練設備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:33.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,上回的選拔考試從963名報名者中挑選了10名在這裡邊參加了考試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個  成為宇航員的條件是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:39.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,首先需要身體健康
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,擅長英語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最重要的是具有協同性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這一點是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:51.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:53.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,發音要稍微再加油一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我們也去向大姐姐問一下小行星的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小行星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:12.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒錯  說不定會成為找到小行星的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:16.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我只是個導覽  詳細的並不是太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:20.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想展示館裡的解說員可能會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:22.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒有的  真是多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好！敵在展示館
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,出發吧  藍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是人工衛星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有隼鳥號的展覽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.35,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：隼鳥號是日本的小行星探測器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:54.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這裡的話一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那個  打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:02.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們想要尋找小行星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,請問你有沒有什麼提示…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:06.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,提示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:10.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,或者您知道對於這方面比較了解的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:17.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這中心基本是宇宙開發活動的展示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,雖然也有小行星探索機器的展示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對於新天體的探索發現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,全國的其他據點的話應該會有這方面的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:31.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:33.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒有找到線索
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是也學到了很多  弄懂了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:46.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比如一個個地去全國的其他據點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,總有一天能遇見這方面的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樂觀過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小櫻  幫得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是看不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你也去幫下她們啊  你的協同性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老師  參觀結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是宇宙食品  有賣各種各樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇宙服仿製品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老師買了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我才是想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那麼  差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,咦  夢露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去洗手間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去了挺久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你這表情怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇宙真是遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:46.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,燒烤已經準備好了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就像是祭典一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:55.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,爺爺在閒暇的時間裡可是很努力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒有帶上你真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,作為道歉  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天是滿月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:13.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對的  所以今天很難看見星星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:17.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這個時候  賞月也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,既然難得  把望遠鏡拿出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,同學們  能稍微幫下忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:24.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哇 架台是赤道儀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:31.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,和地學部的部件不太一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:36.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地學部的架台是轉動橫豎的經緯台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:40.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,爺爺的是隨著地球的自轉轉動的赤道儀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:46.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,赤道儀的話只需要轉動一個旋鈕就能一直鎖定  太方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:54.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原本以為月亮會更坑坑窪窪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼滑溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:02.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是因為滿月的時候  太陽光從正面照射到月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,環形山的突起就很難看清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,順帶一提  環形山比較多的亮部  主要由斜長岩組成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,暗部主要由玄武岩組成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,學了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們也稍微學一下石頭的知識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,拿我們撒氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:28.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂  吃西瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:29.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,西瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是幸拜託我找的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,找到了啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,舊的宣傳單？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:44.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,面向高中生  尋找新天體項目？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:46.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.75,Asteroid - HandWrite4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(820,290)}KIRA星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.75,Asteroid - HandWrite4,,0,0,0,,{\c&H845929&\pos(1466,894)}挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.75,Asteroid - HandWrite4 - up,,0,0,0,,{\pos(820,290)}KIRA星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.75,Asteroid - HandWrite4 - up,,0,0,0,,{\c&H845929&\pos(1466,894)}挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:51.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是暑假時在天文台舉辦的一個叫「KIRA星挑戰」的項目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我以前也參加過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可是那時候沒有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要把這麼厲害的情報藏著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:05.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你們的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是入部的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我在隔壁房間睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:12.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今年的報名截止日期已經過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:18.11,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz15.21\pos(918.8,396.8)}本活動報名已結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.35,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,要是能夠早點發現就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地點在石垣島
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.50,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,果然生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在沖繩啊  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石垣島…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沖繩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,藍色大海…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,KIRA星挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:36.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,參加對象為全國高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,根據提出的課題選出七名參加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:43.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,競爭激烈  而且也不一定能發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:48.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是我感覺稍微前進了一兩步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:49.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也許是大跳了一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:53.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那時候從石垣島回來的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,眼神也和那群孩子一樣閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:12.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,參觀JAXA  BBQ  還有天體觀測
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最後放煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你玩太拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:21.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  沒想到老師曾經參加過尋找小行星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我一直都很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:30.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  天文班三人都更加接近目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,三個都？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想成為宇航員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇航員?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:39.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:40.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以今天才那麼認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是個過於遠大的夢想  有些羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:50.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對自己的夢想說羞恥是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果是認真追求的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對於還沒有確定具體目標的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你們這樣真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對自己的夢想不要顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小櫻  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,並不是在生我們的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我不是在激勵你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太難懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,對自己的夢想不要顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我好像找到了自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,其實  我有一個想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.66,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB39DA0&\pos(345.6,543.6)}地圖和測量科學館
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這裡是繪製地圖的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,國土地理院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,沒想到豬瀨對這方面有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:45.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,雖然原計劃改變了  你們沒意見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:48.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:52.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看到那樣的神情  我想誰都不會抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.69,Asteroid - Chat2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,167)}筑波VLBI天線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,難怪感覺有一些傷感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老師  怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:10.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在那裡原本有一座特別大的碟形天線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這裡有天線哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不再沉溺於過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感覺打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:39.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,通過這次的合宿  了解了學姐們新的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,通過參觀學到了各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感覺大家的世界都變寬闊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:51.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,雖然尋找小行星這一夢想還很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:56.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但像是在河畔找到的  很小的化石一樣的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:57.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一定存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:00.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,存在於這片天空的某處
Comment: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:49.07,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,---OP---
